## Library Usage

Use Sentry CLI programmatically in Node.js (≥22) or Bun without spawning a subprocess:

\```typescript
import sentry from "sentry";

// Returns parsed JSON — same as `sentry issue list --json`
const issues = await sentry("issue", "list", "-l", "5");

